snippet.title: NSMBW Superstar Mode: Beta World 1 Levels
snippet.description:
Back when Superstar Mode was just "NSMBW Master Mode But Complete", I had a friend record these stages for me, Just to never be used for anything because the direction of the mod changed to be more of its own thing. This version of the mod takes place at the end of 2022, when the mod started entering the phase it's in now, But still very NSMBW Master Mode like. 


Music By:
Nintyler (Forest Theme)
NSMBW Master Mode & Mayro (Tower Boss, Castle & Castle Boss)
Nintendo: Anything else

Footage Recorded By: @qualiqola /@qualiqolaarchive 


Team:
VioletNATP
5 Points
JackSnacksOnBigMacs


Superstar Mode Logo, Channel PFP, & Video Border Made By: JackSnacksOnBigMacs
